<L>__{exterior processing station}
<A>__{an infernal engine, roaring out of control. steam blasts and swirls, lightning zaps around the superstructure and columns of incandescent gas thunder hundreds of feet into the air. we approach, hypnotically. the drop ship enters frame, moving toward the station. it pivots, hovering in the blasting turbulence, and settles onto a narrow landing platform ten levels above the ground, or about a third of the way up the enormous structure.}
